query:
SELECT wb.id, wb.branchId, b.nameAr as branchName, wb.year, wb.month, wb.weekNumber, wb.totalAmount, wb.status
FROM weeklyBonuses wb
LEFT JOIN branches b ON wb.branchId = b.id
WHERE wb.year = 2026 AND wb.month = 1 AND wb.weekNumber = 1;
